{
  "id": "adv_main_02_11_01",
  "title": "東京編2章26話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sad-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "トップアイドルになる目標も、星見プロのみんなと\nいつか一緒に歌う夢も、全部……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To become a top idol‚ and the dream of someday\nsinging together with everyone at Hoshimi Pro… everything…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.34
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "全部、失くしちゃいました……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everything‚ I've lost it all…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.5185515676,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "天動さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tendo-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "姫野さんも、ほんと、ようやりますわ……\nあんな嘘のスキャンダルまで用意して……っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Himeno-san‚ she really‚ does this kind of thing…\nEven preparing such a fake scandal…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは分かってくれますよね\n私達、誓ってあんなことしてません。なのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Manager-san‚ you understand us‚ right?\nWe swear we didn't do such a thing. But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "鈴村さん、奥山さん……もちろんだ。信じてるよ\nでも、解雇された事実は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzumura-san‚ Okuyama-san… Of course. I believe you.\nBut‚ the fact that you were fired…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "もう覆せません。でっち上げのスキャンダルで解雇され\nステージという、たった一つの拠り所すら奪われた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't overturn it anymore. I was fired because of a fabricated scandal‚\nand the only thing I had to rely on‚ the stage‚ was also taken away from me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "こんなにもスキャンダルにまみれちゃった私達は\n今後はもう、ステージに立てないんでしょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're so caught up in scandals that\nWe can't stand on the stage anymore‚ can we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことない。あのスキャンダルが事実無根だって\n証明すれば、必ずまた立てる。俺も協力するから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true. If we prove that the scandal is unfounded‚\nWe can definitely stand on stage again. I'll help you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは、ほんまに優しいお人やわ\nせやから、うちらは守りたくなったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Manager-san‚ you're a truly kind person.\nThat's why we wanted to protect you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "姫野さんのやり方に従うつもりなんてなかったけど\n星見プロのみんなを守るには、そうするしか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wasn't going to follow Himeno-san's way‚ but\nTo protect everyone at Hoshimi Pro‚ that was the only way…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "それでも、I-UNITYで\n同じステージに立てるのは、楽しみだったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so‚ I was looking forward to\nbeing able to stand on the same stage at I-UNITY.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "そして立つからには、そういう裏の事情は抜きに\n全力でファンのために歌いたかった……アイドルだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And once we're on stage‚ I wanted to sing with all my might for the fans‚\nwithout any of those behind-the-scenes circumstances… Because I'm an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、その未来は奪われてしまった……\nコンサートライトの光の海も、もう見られない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ that future has been taken away from me…\nI can't see the sea of concert lights anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "歌を届けることも、ファンの声援を聞くことも出来ない\nだから最後に、三人でここに立っていたかったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't deliver my song‚ nor can I hear the cheers of my fans.\nThat's why I wanted to stand here with the three of us one last time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、{user}さんはなんで\n私達がここに居るって分かったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of which‚ manager-san‚ how did you\nknow we were here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 125.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "天動さんの言ってた通りだよ\n三人の気持ちを考えれば、ここに居るだろうって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's just like Tendo-san said.\nI thought that if I considered your feelings‚ you'd be here…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "なんて、そう断言出来てたらかっこいいんだけど\nあちこち探し回って、やっと見つけたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It would've been cool if I could have said that with confidence‚ but\nI searched everywhere and finally found you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "あははっ。{user}さんらしいですね\n見つけてくれて、ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha. That's so like you‚ manager-san.\nThank you for finding us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "そうやっていつも気にかけてくれるのは\n本当に、心から嬉しく思っていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The way you always care about us like that\nmakes me truly happy from the bottom of my heart.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "……けど、これでもう、最後にして下さい\n私達のこれからは、私達三人で決めていきますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But‚ please make this the last time.\nWe'll decide our future from now on‚ the three of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "俺じゃ……俺達じゃ\nトリエルの力になってあげられないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Am I… Are we\nnot able to be a strength for TRINITYAiLE?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
